{"tid":1066424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府高度關注港鐵列車相撞事故　促召開緊急董事局會議","createTime":"2019-03-18T01:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T23:22:37.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9b2f7ce15a86ef6d4486d45be2010c3a644574db","tid":1066424,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1448213_1_20190318093813.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1448213_1_20190318093813.jpg&h=fdbf9703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府高度關注凌晨港鐵兩列列車在荃灣綫新信號系統測試時發生相撞的事故，運輸及房屋局局長陳帆要求港鐵公司徹底調查事故原因，並已聯絡港鐵公司主席馬時亨，提出召開緊急董事局會議的要求。<br />\n<br />\n由於今日港鐵列車服務會受影響，運輸署一直密切監察交通情況，亦已經要求和協調各公共交通營辦商加強服務。"},{"pid":"36f5b9293236c36a4c30f51b39db3e147dcde3cc","tid":1066424,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:42:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448213-20190318.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448213-20190318.htm&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4M6hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=e4882287\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448213-20190318.htm&h=43711946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448213-20190318.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4e134366fb7f9422113c0f0b7e27d0181f899f3c","tid":1066424,"uid":228963,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:43:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85256e728aaacf043087c047dfec5c82a5e150a4","tid":1066424,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:44:07.000Z","msg":"罰錢--&gt;加價落市民度"},{"pid":"17e2cd16d86e170c8e42305bb23655ab35136c36","tid":1066424,"uid":52595,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:44:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33f5e83b58